Pre-Game Insights: Cricket Ireland announced the selection of three men's T20 International squads for the upcoming series against Pakistan, Tri-Series involving Netherlands and Scotland, and the ICC Men's T20 World Cup.
Others: The squad consists of the same 14 players across all three squads, with Josh Little, currently representing the Gujarat Titans in the Indian Premier League, being provisionally included as the 15th squad member for the T20 World Cup.
